file.name: api.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 0.1.0
  title: Test

paths:
  "/foobar":
    post:
      operationId: MyOp
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                foo:
                  type: string
      responses:
        201:
          description: foobar
    put:
      operationId: MySecondOp
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
      responses:
        201:
          description: foobar
  "/foobar2":
    post:
      operationId: MyOp2
      responses:
        201:
          description: foobar

components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: object
